Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveNollywood actress, Tonto Dikeh, has expressed happiness at Ghana beating Nigeria to qualify for the 2022 World Cup.
On her verified Instagram account, she said “I’m so happy for Ghana honestly. As much as I love my people, omo Nigerians we brag too much abeg. Honestly wish they gave us like 3-1 to add some salt to the injury.”
The actress added, “After all, I am Ghanaian by love. Failure is also a win if you think about it deeply, we are too distracted to take leadership come 2023.”
